exercises.name: High Standing Crunch
exercises.description: Using high suspended bands from standing position, bring your back forward, pulling down your arms

exercises.name: High Downward Oblique Swing - Left and Right
exercises.description: Using high suspended bands from standing position, rotate body while pulling bands across. Should result in a full 180 rotation. Switch between sets

exercises.name: Middle Pallof Press
exercises.description: Using middle suspended bands, standing with arms out, grab both band handholds and push out at an angle. Band should never be slack. Alternate between

exercises.name: Middle 180 Twists
exercises.description: Using middle suspended bands, standing with arms in front, grab both band handholds with both hands and make a large combined fist. Rotate your midsection from 90 degrees right to 90 degress left, and back.

exercises.name: Low Downward Oblique Swing - Left and Right
exercises.description: Using low suspended bands from standing position, with fists together, rotate body while pulling bands across and up your body. Should result in a full 180 rotation. Switch between sets

exercises.name: Low Deadbug Dual Knee Ins
exercises.description: Lying down with hands on both low tight, suspended bands, bring knees up to your chest and back to lying down position
